---
import Windmillsvg from '@/components/Windmillsvg.astro'

---

<section class="bg-coolGray-100 py-24 overflow-hidden" id="windmill-container">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl tracking-tight mb-6">The Framework</h2>
    <p class="text-coolGray-60 mb-10">
      Like a windmill, an organization creates momentum when every part moves in balance. People, process, and product each play a different role, but they only create lasting value when they work together. Empowered teams, principles-led ways of working, and a strong product direction help turn effort into outcomes, not just output.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-5/12 px-4">
        <Windmillsvg />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full lg:w-7/12 px-4 lg:mt-0 self-center">
        <div class="max-w-lg xl:max-w-none mx-auto lg:mr-0 pt-6">
          <button class="group block text-left w-full pb-6 mb-8 border-b" id="btnpeople">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block mr-8 text-sm">01</span>
              <span class="inline-block text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl">People</span>
              <span class="group-hover:rotate-270 w-6 h-6 lg:group-hover:rotate-225 transform transition duration-100 ml-auto">
                <svg viewbox="0 0 33 33" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-primary-600 dark:stroke-primary-600">
                  <path d="M30 3L3 30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4.3875" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                  <path d="M30 27.758V3H5.24196" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4.3875" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 pr-10 hidden details">
              <p>
                People are where momentum starts. Empowered, cross-functional teams need trust, ownership, and clear strategic context so they can make good decisions, collaborate deeply, and solve meaningful problems for customers and the business.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-6 text-right">
                <a href="/category/people/" class="group inline-flex items-center leading-none font-medium pb-2 border-b-2 border-black dark:border-white" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">
                  <span class="mr-4">Explore People posts</span>
                  <span class="group-hover:rotate-45 transform transition duration-100">
                    <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-primary-600 dark:stroke-primary-600">
                      <path d="M9.5 1.5L1.5 9.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                      <path d="M9.5 8.83571V1.5H2.16429" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </button>
          <button class="group block w-full text-left pb-6 mb-8 border-b" id="btnprocess">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block mr-8 text-sm">02</span>
              <span class="inline-block text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl">Process</span>
              <span class="group-hover:rotate-270 w-6 h-6 lg:group-hover:rotate-225 transform transition duration-100 ml-auto">
                <svg viewbox="0 0 33 33" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-primary-600 dark:stroke-primary-600">
                  <path d="M30 3L3 30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4.3875" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                  <path d="M30 27.758V3H5.24196" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4.3875" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 pr-10 hidden details">
              <p>
                Process keeps the movement steady, but it should never become the goal itself. The best ways of working are guided by principles, reduce friction, support discovery and delivery, and help teams learn fast while staying accountable for outcomes.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-6 text-right">
                <a href="/category/process/" class="group inline-flex items-center leading-none font-medium pb-2 border-b-2 border-black dark:border-white" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">
                  <span class="mr-4">Explore Process posts</span>
                  <span class="group-hover:rotate-45 transform transition duration-100">
                    <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-primary-600 dark:stroke-primary-600">
                      <path d="M9.5 1.5L1.5 9.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                      <path d="M9.5 8.83571V1.5H2.16429" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </button>
          <button class="group block w-full text-left" id="btnproduct">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block mr-8 text-sm">03</span>
              <span class="inline-block text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl">Product</span>
              <span class="group-hover:rotate-270 w-6 h-6 lg:group-hover:rotate-225 transform transition duration-100 ml-auto">
                <svg viewbox="0 0 33 33" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-primary-600 dark:stroke-primary-600">
                  <path d="M30 3L3 30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4.3875" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                  <path d="M30 27.758V3H5.24196" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4.3875" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 pr-10 hidden details">
              <p>
                Product is the value created from that movement. It is not just a roadmap of features to ship, but a set of problems to solve: valuable for customers, usable in practice, feasible to build, and viable for the business.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-6 text-right">
                <a href="/category/product/" class="group inline-flex items-center leading-none font-medium pb-2 border-b-2 border-black dark:border-white" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">
                  <span class="mr-4">Explore Product posts</span>
                  <span class="group-hover:rotate-45 transform transition duration-100">
                    <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-primary-600 dark:stroke-primary-600">
                      <path d="M9.5 1.5L1.5 9.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                      <path d="M9.5 8.83571V1.5H2.16429" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>